claim.claim-text:
A machine for manufacturing a roll of multi-layer price tags, said machine having a proximal end and a distal end, said machine comprising:
a base;
a frame attached to said base toward the distal end of said machine;
a secondary frame attached to said base toward the proximal end of said machine;
an unwinder mounted to said frame toward the distal end of said machine;
at least two printers mounted to said frame;
at least one automated label applicator mounted to said frame between said at least two printers; and
a rewinder mounted to said secondary frame.

A machine for manufacturing a plurality of individual multi-layer price tags, said machine having a proximal end and a distal end, said machine comprising:
a base;
a frame attached to said base toward the distal end of said machine;
a secondary frame attached to said base toward the proximal end of said machine;
an unwinder mounted to said frame toward the proximal end of said machine;
at least two printers mounted to said frame;
at least one automated label applicator mounted to said frame between said at least two printers; and
and an automated label cutter mounted to said secondary frame.
